58:24.320 --> 58:27.800
* I've found a new place to dwell

58:30.520 --> 58:34.360
* Down at the end of Lonely Street

58:36.040 --> 58:38.400
* Heartbreak Hotel

58:39.600 --> 58:44.800
* Oh, feeling so lonely, baby

58:46.080 --> 58:50.630
* Feeling so lonely, baby

58:50.680 --> 58:53.600
* I could die... *

